    "(11)-(14).",
    "Table 4 summarizes recent WPP studies and their adopted learning schemes.",
    "Next, we will conduct a comprehensive review on four components, f sp (⋅), f c (⋅), f fe (⋅), and f o (⋅), of WPP methods.",
    "In WPP studies, time series inputs are typically treated as a signal.",
    "Therefore, advanced signal processing methods may better capture the patterns of the input time series from different perspectives."
